OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FThe Conservatives will introduce a
OL,7,FWelsh winter fuel payment if they win
OL,8,Fthe next Senedd election, the party
OL,9,Fleader is to announce.
OL,11,FWelsh Tories will meet in Llangollen
OL,12,Fon Friday for their annual party
OL,13,Fconference, with Darren Millar
OL,14,Fpromising the party will have the
OL,15,F"boldest" manifesto next year.
OL,17,FDuring the two-day event, they will
OL,18,Fmake several announcements, including
OL,19,Fpledging to introduce a Welsh winter
OL,20,Ffuel payment if they win the next
OL,21,FWelsh Parliament election in May 2026.
