OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FWinter fuel payments were previously
OL,7,Fgiven to all pensioners across the UK.
OL,9,FHowever, last year, the UK Labour
OL,10,Fgovernment restricted the payments to
OL,11,Fthose qualifying for pension credits
OL,12,Fand other income-related benefits, as
OL,13,Fpart of a bid to close a black hole in
OL,14,Fthe nation's finances.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Conservatives will also
OL,17,Fpledge to cut the basic rate of income
OL,18,Ftax by 1p, fuelled through efficiency
OL,19,Fmeasures across government
OL,20,Fdepartments, while protecting health,
OL,21,Fschools and farming.
