OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FAll road projects will be "unfrozen"
OL,7,Fand no new cycle lanes will be built
OL,8,Funtil "roads are fixed".
OL,10,FMr Millar's party will also pledge to
OL,11,Freverse the expansion of the Senedd,
OL,12,Fwhich is due to increase to 96 members
OL,13,Ffrom 60 after the election.
OL,15,FThe conference is one of the last
OL,16,Fchances for the party to get together
OL,17,Fbefore the election next year, and
OL,18,Fcomes at a time when the Conservatives
OL,19,Fare struggling in the polls in Wales.
