OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FA recent Barn Cymru poll by YouGov for
OL,7,FITV Cymru Wales and Cardiff University
OL,8,Fput the Welsh Tories in fourth place
OL,9,Fon 13% at the next Senedd election,
OL,10,Fbehind Plaid Cymru, Reform UK and
OL,11,FLabour.
OL,13,FMr Millar MS said: "The Welsh
OL,14,FConservative 2026 manifesto will be
OL,15,Fthe boldest and most ambitious in our
OL,16,Fhistory.
OL,18,F"My team and I will present a
OL,19,Fcomprehensive, fully-funded set of
OL,20,Fpolicy commitments to fix Wales ahead
OL,21,Fof the Senedd election.
