OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives are working
OL,7,Ftirelessly to hold Labour to account,
OL,8,Fwhile other parties like Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fhave routinely propped them up.
OL,11,F"We now stand ready to offer the only
OL,12,Fcredible alternative Welsh government."
OL,14,FAnalysis by Rob Osborne, ITV Wales
OL,15,FNational Correspondent,
OL,17,FThe Conservative Party has come to
OL,18,Ftown, Llangollen, to be precise.
OL,20,FWelsh leader Darren Millar is here. So
OL,21,Fis the UK leader Kemi Badenoch.
