OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FBut hovering over the conference is
OL,7,Fthe man who isn't here: Nigel Farage.
OL,8,FMany Conservatives fear he could
OL,9,Fdestroy their support in Wales.
OL,11,FBased on our most recent poll, they
OL,12,Fmay be right.
OL,14,FReform UK is attracting votes from
OL,15,Fdisillusioned Conservative supporters.
OL,16,FThe Conservatives now risk falling
OL,17,Ffrom the main opposition to fourth
OL,18,Fplace.
