OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,F"It could be worse," some party
OL,7,Fmembers say with a brave face, but
OL,8,Fnext to total annihilation, it's hard
OL,9,Fto see how.
OL,11,FNot that you'll hear any of this said
OL,12,Fpublicly this weekend.JThe message is
OL,13,Fone of defiance: take the fight to
OL,14,FReform, Labour and Plaid Cymru.
OL,16,FBut bubbling beneath the surface is a
OL,17,Fdeeper split in the Conservative ranks.
