OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FDarren Millar has declared he'd be
OL,7,Fwilling to work with any party to
OL,8,Fremove Labour from power in Cardiff
OL,9,FBay, including Plaid Cymru.
OL,11,FThat stance has angered some
OL,12,Fgrassroots Conservatives, who see it
OL,13,Fas a betrayal of core values.
OL,15,FMany have expressed their frustrations
OL,16,Fonline.
OL,18,FAnd now one of them, prominent
OL,19,Factivist Huw Davies, says he's been
OL,20,Fsuspended from the party, without
OL,21,Fbeing told why.
