OL,3,CWelsh Tories in vow to introduce
OL,4,Cwinter fuel payment, if elected
OL,6,FSome suspect it's linked to his
OL,7,Foutspoken criticism of the Welsh
OL,8,FConservatives' direction.JMeanwhile,
OL,9,Fanother fracture line is emerging:
OL,10,Fdevolution.
OL,12,FWhile the leadership insists the party
OL,13,Fsupports Welsh devolution, a vocal
OL,14,Fgroup of activists want that position
OL,15,Freversed.
OL,17,FThere are blue skies in Llangollen
OL,18,Ftoday, but there could be a stormy few
OL,19,Fdays ahead for the Welsh Conservatives.
